      • createEquivalenceLinks

        public void createEquivalenceLinks(java.util.List<java.util.List<WTPart>> downstreamPartPaths,
                                   java.util.List<java.util.List<WTPart>> upstreamPartPaths,
                                   wt.associativity.NCServerHolder downstreamNCServerHolder,
                                   wt.associativity.NCServerHolder upstreamNCServerHolder)
                            throws WTException,
                                   WTPropertyVetoException
        Create Equivalence Links between all selected upstream and downstream PartPaths. (If there are N upstream Part paths and M downstream Part paths, we will potentially create N * M equivalence links) Duplicate upstream/downstream selected Parts are removed, and we use the "common equivalence contexts" algorithm to compute the new equivalence links' upstream/downstream contexts.

        Supported API: true
        Parameters:
        downstreamPartPaths -
        upstreamPartPaths -
        downstreamNCServerHolder -
        upstreamNCServerHolder -
        Throws:
        WTException
        WTPropertyVetoException
